⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Fell God's Flame
node ER · ER · ⟦The Fell God's Flame:ER:9b79d3⟧

WHO   — The Fell God's Flame — the fire that burns the Erdtree
WHAT  — The flame of the Fell God, Outer God of the Fire Giants — the one fire that can burn the Erdtree.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the Mountaintops of the Giants · the Forge of the Giants  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It is the destroying flame — the only fire the Erdtree fears, and the fire the Tarnished must set to the Erdtree's base to walk the path of the game's ending.
HOW   — Chained but never extinguished, it waits as the Flame of Ruin in the Forge of the Giants, tended forever by the cursed last giant and watched by the Fire Monks.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Every order keeps one fire it cannot put out — only chain, and watch, and wait.

